data.description: Welcome to Embers! This lovely southern exposure pool home is situated on a spacious corner lot with 3 bedrooms and 3 full baths. Ten foot ceilings throughout combined with natural light streaming through the windows makes this home feel larger than it is. Boasting a beautiful pool/spa & patio area with southern exposure, where you can bask in the warm, natural light from sunrise to sunset. The heart of this home is undoubtedly the large kitchen, which is a chef's dream come true. Featuring a generous island, ample counter space, and a plethora of cabinetry, you'll have everything you need to prepare gourmet meals, entertain guests, or simply enjoy an intimate meal. For those who love boating & water adventures, you're just 1.7 miles away from the Burnt Store public boat ramp, offering easy access to the Gulf of Mexico. Families will appreciate the proximity of Oasis North Elementary and Mariner schools less than 2 miles away as well as the Northwest public library. ** Seller has an assumable VA mortgage at 2.75% interest.**
